Comment: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{3:12 title}Sympathetic Vibration
Comment: 0,0:05:26.84,0:05:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{5:38}The shelter is this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.51,0:00:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai... don't tell me you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.15,0:00:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.34,0:00:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.96,0:00:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.14,0:00:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Terrorists, eh? St-State your conditions!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.22,0:00:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.83,0:01:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm GHQ's Supreme Commander—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.37,0:01:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unit number 823.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.34,0:01:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same number as my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.11,0:01:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.64,0:01:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... you don't even get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.93,0:01:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two are obscene!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{SO EVERYTHING THAT MAKES ME WHORE}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.56,0:03:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Keido Shuichiro, chief of GHQ's Anti Bodies unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid that Major General Yan has died tragically today
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in a surprise terrorist attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.82,0:03:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You worked hard, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.59,0:03:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In accordance with military regulations,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as the highest-ranking official at the scene,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.23,0:03:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be assuming command.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.14,0:03:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These terrorists have launched a despicable, large-scale viral attack
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.82,0:03:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,against the entire Kanto region.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a Level 1 state of emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.41,0:03:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As of this moment, all military personnel are under Anti Bodies command.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I repeat: This is a Level 1 state of emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.67,0:03:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll avail ourselves of your help as well, Dr. Ouma.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.06,0:03:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.22,0:03:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruka! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.50,0:04:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you point your gun at a woman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.83,0:04:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I expected more from you, Scarface!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.90,0:04:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bit behind, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.01,0:04:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I expected more from you from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time to move, Major Segai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.93,0:04:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}At approximately 3:40 pm,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.47,0:04:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}a terrorist group calling itself the Undertakers
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}carried out a large-scale attack at Haneda Airport using the Virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's wrong!{overlapping}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.11,0:04:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}In response, the government has issued a special contagion alert,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.41,0:04:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Undertakers would never resort to bioterrorism!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.77,0:04:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, {\i1}duh{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.10,0:04:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}and citizens are...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.61,0:04:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.14,0:04:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Shu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've taken us all down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:04:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I can't get in touch with Gai or Inoreen...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.89,0:04:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, we'll all...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:04:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's {\i1}your{\i0} fault, Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.84,0:05:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you wouldn't come!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.96,0:05:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you wouldn't use Voids!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.63,0:05:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}A special contagion alert has been issued.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}All students who haven't yet evacuated,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.65,0:05:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen Hare and Ouma?{overlapping}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.65,0:05:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}please move to your designated shelter blocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu probably went home early.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.61,0:05:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I repeat: A special contagion alert has been...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.23,0:05:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was looking pretty sick earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.60,0:05:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they can hear this broadcast,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.16,0:05:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like the following people to, um... to report to the Film Club room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.36,0:05:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's a bad time, but I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.15,0:05:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll use their Voids to save Gai and Inori.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know whether I can really do it or not, but I've got no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.10,0:05:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The leader, Tsutsugami Gai, is on the run with one accomplice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.23,0:05:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Undertakers' remaining arsenal consists of one large trailer, one Endlave,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.39,0:06:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a fighting force of about eight people west of the terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.33,0:06:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've completely lost their chain of command now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.90,0:06:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He just arrived in Roppongi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.82,0:06:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems Undertakers' forces are concentrated at Haneda,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.15,0:06:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just as planned.{KEIKAKU DOORI}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.39,0:06:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to cross the river of lamentation...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.93,0:06:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.16,0:06:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this "favor," Shu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.07,0:06:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know we're under a contagion alert, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.86,0:06:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hmm. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to go to Haneda.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the airport?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.07,0:06:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Virus is out there, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.89,0:06:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.81,0:06:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,people I want to save at Haneda.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.06,0:06:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't do it by myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.90,0:06:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so, I thought if I could get your help...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:06:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you intend to use people like tools again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.91,0:07:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "tools"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.14,0:07:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.34,0:07:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe Shu will answer that for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, Shu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.61,0:07:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mana...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.65,0:07:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we're doing this again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.65,0:07:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.08,0:07:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could stop this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.19,0:07:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.38,0:07:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After it's crystallized this much, even your blood won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.22,0:07:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I mean I could sing that song...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.73,0:07:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inori?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.91,0:07:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a lot of questions for you, but for now tell me this:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.68,0:07:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Shu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.08,0:07:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.44,0:07:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We left him behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.24,0:07:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He should be in school right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.94,0:08:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... he'll come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.03,0:08:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that... Shu will...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0020,,Might I ask what he means by "tools," exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.64,0:08:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0020,,Who is it you have to go save, even when it's this dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.37,0:08:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0020,,Don't tell me it's Inori?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0020,,Is it Inori?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.70,0:08:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0020,,Don't all go at him at once, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.29,0:08:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu will answer you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.20,0:08:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.34,0:08:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What would Gai do at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.38,0:08:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Would he act without taking no for an answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.71,0:08:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time! We have to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.27,0:08:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, tell us, Shu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.09,0:08:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're friends, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.88,0:08:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouma Shu, I believe you have a duty to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.52,0:08:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Would he get some consensus first?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.49,0:08:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Would he trick them into doing what he wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.71,0:08:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or would he just force orders on them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.57,0:08:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's Gai's way of doing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be like Gai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll just have to do things the way I can do them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.75,0:09:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hare.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.67,0:09:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm about to do something a little scary to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.53,0:09:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.71,0:09:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.33,0:09:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.72,0:09:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.76,0:09:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.48,0:09:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.04,0:09:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bandaging... That's like you, Hare.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Hare?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:09:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.76,0:09:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll wake up when I put this back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on, Shu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.37,0:10:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I trust you'll explain, Ouma?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.36,0:10:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a Void.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.96,0:10:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's someone's heart given form.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.84,0:10:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So its shape and effects will be different depending on the person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.46,0:10:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.31,0:10:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What did I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.12,0:10:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.49,0:10:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used your Void just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.40,0:10:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did mine look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.35,0:10:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was kind, like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.55,0:10:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure you've forgotten,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.51,0:10:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I've drawn out yours before, too, Souta and Yahiro... and Kuhouin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.59,0:10:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Us too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.48,0:11:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It felt like I'd peeked into your hearts without asking, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've felt guilty all along.{WHOAH HO TITLE DROP}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.27,0:11:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not all, though, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.68,0:11:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You forgot the part where you used that power to help terrorists.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.41,0:11:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.14,0:11:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.31,0:11:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say who you want to go save now, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.17,0:11:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.09,0:11:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai and Inori... everyone in the Undertakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inori's in the Undertakers too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.74,0:11:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me, Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.76,0:11:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you want to save people like that? {autistic colon removed}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.16,0:11:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you couldn't even save Jun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.97,0:11:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys are {\i1}terrorists{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.62,0:11:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because they believed that there was something I could do!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.13,0:11:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it hadn't been for the Undertakers, I'd still be someone who didn't matter! {>implying that isn't the case}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.79,0:11:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now they're in trouble, and there's something I can do to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.16,0:11:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So {\i1}please{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.14,0:12:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.43,0:12:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No guarantee we'll be safe here anyway, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.25,0:12:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Might as well move, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just like you, Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like it's not someone else's business for me, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.64,0:12:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.43,0:12:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Yahiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.46,0:12:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I never would've mattered either, if Jun hadn't needed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.91,0:12:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the same, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.32,0:12:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{eyecatch}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.73,0:12:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the Gate of Hell that leads to Cocytus?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.75,0:12:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.83,0:12:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For me, this is the Gate of Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.36,0:12:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hold out very long!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.53,0:13:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I'd do the practical test under {\i1}these{\i0} circumstances...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.32,0:13:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will Shu come?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.14,0:13:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do I... want him to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0090,,I didn't know there was a pathway here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.51,0:13:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0090,,We should be able to get close to the airport
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.51,0:13:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0090,,without getting stopped by the army this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.10,0:13:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all right now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.36,0:13:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.18,0:13:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I owe it to you, Hare.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.35,0:13:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, dammit, {\i1}dammit{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.04,0:14:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost there... Almost there!{i've split over 30 lines so far. i'm tired of this shit so no more. after all, a crappy show deserves a crappy script.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.89,0:14:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's open!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.42,0:14:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inori!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.36,0:14:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'll never be loved by you again
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.99,0:14:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Or needed by you again, either
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}And so here I am, all alone
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:15:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You always do that, make me angry
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.57,0:15:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}And then make me cry in the end
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.83,0:15:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}But when you said "I'm sorry" afterward,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inori.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.14,0:15:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Genomic resonance is exceeding 3000?! {try tripling that first}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.63,0:15:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I always loved the look on your face
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.55,0:15:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This song...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Inori.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inori's singing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a barricade up ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.01,0:15:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.97,0:15:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll eliminate all intruders by force!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuhouin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.02,0:15:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.40,0:15:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yes, hold me tight as you can and don't let go
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.20,0:15:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barricade 3 has been breached!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.18,0:15:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it an Endlave?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:15:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, er...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:16:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I want to be in your arms
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.68,0:16:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}We'll sleep with our foreheads pressed together
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.15,0:16:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.57,0:16:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai wouldn't retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.05,0:16:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hare!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.49,0:16:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're swarming us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.37,0:16:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Souta, it's your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.90,0:16:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.06,0:16:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You always do that, make me angry
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.83,0:16:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Endlave Platoon 4 has been completely wiped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.36,0:16:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gate 2 has been breached!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:17:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't stop one measly buggy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.56,0:17:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}And then make me cry in the end
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.18,0:17:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How incompetent can you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Swap me into the nearest unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.87,0:17:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}But when you said "I'm sorry" afterward,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.63,0:17:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I always loved the look on your face
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.20,0:17:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.48,0:17:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.98,0:17:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi! The radar building!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.12,0:17:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye-aye! We'll take the shortest route!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.39,0:17:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.02,0:17:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.58,0:17:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.39,0:17:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inori!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.55,0:17:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yes, hold me tight as you can and don't let go
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.12,0:18:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I want to be in your arms
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.72,0:18:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}We'll sleep with our foreheads pressed together
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.89,0:18:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.04,0:18:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what you can do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.50,0:18:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on out, you little rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.55,0:18:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was you, faceless bastard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.14,0:18:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moron. Just wasting my effort...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.89,0:18:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inori!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.03,0:19:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inori.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.04,0:19:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inori!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.17,0:19:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very disappointed in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.49,0:20:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gain what could be your throne, and then you just leave it empty forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.29,0:20:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where we part.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.62,0:20:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, Ouma Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.80,0:20:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The song...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.91,0:20:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.48,0:20:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I can't leave you... to your own devices...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.52,0:20:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai! Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.56,0:21:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.25,0:21:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai!{yes, this show is gay. we know.}
